CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 10, 1954, page 21, reads: "Center Section - The persons present unanimously adopted the resolutions presented."
TitMainTitle: Audience of men, women, and children, gathered for the police brutality meeting in the center section of Bethel AME Church on Webster Avenue in the Hill District
